    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PaceBreak is a fast-paced parkour speedrunning game built around competition. Every movement, jump, and landing matters. Improvements of just a few milliseconds can separate good runs from the best. The game rewards mastery, consistency, and optimization.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chase medals, beat your friends’ times, and climb the leaderboards by refining your routes and movement. PaceBreak is designed for players who enjoy pushing systems to their limits and shaving off time run after run.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced first-person Parkour gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Official Maps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ghost Replays</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Singleplayer and Multiplayer Level-Editor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Workshop Maps</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SMOOTH MOVEMENT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330570/extras/f7b3ac62bcf6092bbc378b29de82bc87.poster.avif?t=1768956942\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330570/extras/f7b3ac62bcf6092bbc378b29de82bc87.webm?t=1768956942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330570/extras/f7b3ac62bcf6092bbc378b29de82bc87.mp4?t=1768956942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Movement is designed to feel as precise, smooth and natural as possible. Build speed through multiple techniques and optimize your path to the top. Flow through the course  effortlessly with momentum that snowballs from move to move.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LEVEL-EDITOR</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330570/extras/e6d53865c7e89380c1a9aff99ef0dbf7.poster.avif?t=1768956942\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330570/extras/e6d53865c7e89380c1a9aff99ef0dbf7.webm?t=1768956942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330570/extras/e6d53865c7e89380c1a9aff99ef0dbf7.mp4?t=1768956942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build and upload your own maps with our in-game level-editor. Features like multiple textures per object, grouping and a limitless map size gives you full creative freedom. Build <strong>solo</strong> or <strong>together with friends</strong>. Or jump into your level while friends are still constructing it. All official levels are made using the level-editor.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WORKSHOP MAPS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330570/extras/b635aba60599ab9a5c69f7b8f4fe9ee5.poster.avif?t=1768956942\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330570/extras/b635aba60599ab9a5c69f7b8f4fe9ee5.webm?t=1768956942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330570/extras/b635aba60599ab9a5c69f7b8f4fe9ee5.mp4?t=1768956942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Download and play maps created by other users using the Steam-Workshop.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BETTER WITH FRIENDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330570/extras/1d5eea247d7565bf15c2699cd102ede9.poster.avif?t=1768956942\" width=1170 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330570/extras/1d5eea247d7565bf15c2699cd102ede9.webm?t=1768956942\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330570/extras/1d5eea247d7565bf15c2699cd102ede9.mp4?t=1768956942\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join your friends in racing for a better time or creating maps with seamless online-support.</p>",
